# wq-health Project Standards

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React 19 + Vite + TypeScript
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Storage)
- **UI**: Tailwind CSS + Radix UI + shadcn/ui
- **Game Engine**: React Flow for visual game builder

## Core Principles
- TypeScript strict mode - never use `any`
- Security-first: RLS policies on all Supabase tables
- Performance: Code splitting, lazy loading, memoization
- Accessibility: WCAG 2.1 AA compliance
- Mobile-first responsive design

## Database Schema
- UUID primary keys (never auto-increment)
- Foreign key constraints on all relations
- RLS policies for multi-tenant isolation
- JSONB for flexible game configs

